These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, plum, pear, avocado
City: berlin, san-francisco, venice, hamburg
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating radish##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person eating radish is the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Food    | plum  | avocado | pear    | radish       |
| City         | san-francisco | hamburg    | venice      | berlin |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, 7up, milk
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, cat, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the owner of the bird##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Beverage        | 7up   | iced-tea | mirinda     | milk      |
| Pet         | frog | cat | mouse | bird |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, goldfish, fish, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, swimming, biathlon, golf
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the russian is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the owner of the horse is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Pet         | horse | goldfish | fish | mouse |
| Sport   | golf       | swimming    | basketball | biathlon     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

