.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, gospel, ambient, reggae
House: art-deco, craftsman, victorian, modern
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the fan of ambient is the person driving the train##1
2. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
5. the victorian house is on the far right##1
6. the art-deco house is the fan of ambient##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the left of the victorian house##1
8. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | blues | reggae | ambient | gospel |
| House       | craftsman     | modern      | art-deco     | victorian      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

