1. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who likes mauve is the owner of the dog##1
7. the person who likes emerald is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Color         | amber   | emerald | fuchsia  | mauve      |
| Pet   | goldfish  | cat        | hedgehog  | dog       |
| Sport         | badminton | climbing    | biathlon | snowboarding |

