.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, purple, amber, black
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, coffee, iced-tea
1. the person who likes white is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who likes black##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person who likes amber##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the person who likes black is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Color           | purple | amber | black | white |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate     | coffee | sprite       |

