.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, december, july
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, journalist, software-developer, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
1. the software-developer is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the journalist is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the project-manager is on the right of the journalist##1
8. the journalist is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday          | may  | july | december   | october     |
| Job         | manager | journalist   | project-manager  | software-developer |
| Movie-Genre   | spy         | disaster  | mystery | thriller  |

