.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
House: futuristic, gothic-revival, farmhouse, ranch-style
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, drama, mystery
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, water-polo, snowboarding, rowing
1. the gothic-revival house is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the farmhouse house##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
8. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| House      | ranch-style | farmhouse     | futuristic | gothic-revival |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation | drama       | crime    |
| Sport   | water-polo   | rowing | sailing    | snowboarding |

