4. the person driving the subway is the futuristic house##1
5. the futuristic house is on the right of the fan of punk##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| House          | farmhouse        | ranch-style   | futuristic  | tower   |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | punk     | d&b    | jazz       |
