.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, family, fantasy, scientific
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, tea, 7up
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, car, scooter, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person drinking tea is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Movie-Genre         | musical  | scientific | family  | fantasy |
| Beverage       | tea | milk        | 7up | mirinda       |
| Transport   | airplane   | car          | tram          | scooter       |

