.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, cooking, dancing, traveling
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, water-polo, swimming, golf
City: hannover, prague, hamburg, boston
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person traveling to hamburg##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling   | dancing   | card-games | cooking |
| Sport   | swimming | biathlon | water-polo   | golf |
| City   | boston     | hannover  | hamburg  | prague  |

