.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle, frog, guinea-pig
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, alhambra, fonseca, siglo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, skateboarding, skiing
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the siglo-smoker##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | turtle    | lizard        | frog |
| Cigar   | alhambra     | fonseca     | siglo        | swisher   |
| Sport         | sailing   | lacrosse | skateboarding | skiing  |

