.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret, chinchilla, lizard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, rock, gospel
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, motorbike, roller
1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of rock##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
8. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Pet   | ferret   | lizard  | hamster    | chinchilla    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | rock  | ambient  | r&b |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter | motorbike | car        |

