.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, tea, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, white, apricot, blue
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, swisher, old-henry, aristoff
1. the game-smoker is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person who likes blue is the person drinking water##1
6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
7. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes purple##1
8. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee        | water    | iced-tea | tea      |
| Color   | purple        | blue   | white  | apricot  |
| Cigar         | aristoff | swisher | old-henry   | game |

