.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer, scientist, security-guard
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, iced-tea, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, december, june
1. the engineer is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
7. the security-guard is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | engineer  | scientist  | dressmaker | security-guard |
| Beverage   | tea   | fanta | coffee   | iced-tea      |
| Birthday         | august | december    | september   | june         |

 